Schedule Check

Want to know if your Department’s Fall 2018 schedule abides by the scheduling rules adopted by FAS? Upload your data here to see, as well as get scheduling analytics.

The course scheduling tool provides a way for departments to ensure that they are offering balanced classes in terms of start time, meetings per week, and what days they are on.
